<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,933,1464]" pageId="2">
Described for the single female from 
<collectingCountry box="[570,687,933,959]" name="Singapore" pageId="2">Singapore</collectingCountry>
. More females were collected recently in West 
<collectingCountry box="[1216,1323,933,959]" name="Malaysia" pageId="2">Malaysia</collectingCountry>
: 
<collectingRegion box="[1333,1397,933,959]" country="Malaysia" name="Johor" pageId="2">Johor</collectingRegion>
, 
<quantity metricMagnitude="4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" pageId="2" unit="km" value="15.0">15 km</quantity>
NW Kota Tinggi, Muntahak Mt, 
<geoCoordinate box="[556,638,969,995]" degrees="1" direction="north" minutes="49" orientation="latitude" pageId="2" precision="925" value="1.8166666">1°49‘N</geoCoordinate>
<geoCoordinate box="[644,755,969,995]" degrees="103" direction="east" minutes="48" orientation="longitude" pageId="2" precision="925" value="103.8">103°48‘E</geoCoordinate>
, 
<quantity box="[765,837,969,996]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="2" unit="m" value="200.0">200 m</quantity>
, 
<date box="[847,1009,969,995]" pageId="2" value="2001-05-13" valueMax="2001-05-14" valueMin="2001-05-13">13.–14.v.2001</date>
, M. Říha leg. (
<specimenCount box="[1172,1284,969,996]" pageId="2" type="female">9 females</specimenCount>
). Finally both sexes were collected in 
<collectingCountry box="[417,530,1005,1031]" name="Indonesia" pageId="2">Indonesia</collectingCountry>
: SW 
<collectingRegion box="[590,724,1005,1031]" country="Indonesia" name="Kalimantan Utara" pageId="2">Kalimantan</collectingRegion>
, Singkawang region, Mt. Bawang, Madi village, 
<quantity box="[1274,1431,1005,1032]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.25" metricValueMax="1.5" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="2" unit="m" value="1250.0" valueMax="1500.0" valueMin="1000.0">1000–1500 m</quantity>
, 
<date box="[151,224,1041,1067]" pageId="2" value="2018-01">i.2018</date>
, local collector (
<specimenCount box="[411,501,1041,1067]" pageId="2" type="male">6 males</specimenCount>
, 
<specimenCount box="[512,620,1041,1067]" pageId="2" type="female">3 females</specimenCount>
- some in copula).
</paragraph>
